
! Madeirado Slitaz (Pack) Theme
! By: HolkFoor (https://twitter.com/holkfoor)
! Version: 1.0-20130701

========================================================

1. INSTALL Madeirado Slim Theme

a) Install Slim Theme
   Directory: /usr/share/slim/themes

b) Config Slim Theme
   File: /etc/slim.conf
   Line: current_theme

========================================================

2. INSTALL Madeirado GTK2 & Openbox Themes

a) Install GTK2 & Openbox
   Directory: /usr/share/themes
   Optional : /home/$USER/.themes

========================================================

3. INSTALL Madeirado Wallpaper

a) You can install the wallpaper in some directory. 
   Or install in /usr/share/backgrounds

========================================================

  Thank you for using Madeirado theme.
